      "last_action_date": "2009-05-11",
      "last_action": "Carried over to 2010 Regular Session.",
      "title": "Temporary Restraining Orders",
      "description": "Requires temporary restraining orders issued by district court to apply to both the petitioner and the respondent. Establishes the \"clear and convincing\" evidentiary threshold for conviction."
