      "last_action": "Carried over to 2010 Regular Session.",
      "title": "Works of Art Special Fund; Appropriation Transfer; Suspension",
      "description": "Suspends until June 30, 2011, the transfer of 1% of all capital improvement project appropriations to the Works of Art Special Fund. Requires any unexpended and unencumbered moneys in the Special Fund on June 30, 2009, be transferred to the appropriate capital projects fund to be allotted and expended for capital improvement projects. (HB1224 HD1)"
