      "last_action": "(H) The committees on TRN recommend that the measure be HELD. The votes were as follows: 9 Ayes: Representative(s) Souki, Awana, Aquino, Hanohano, Keith-Agaran, M. Lee, Nakashima, Takumi, Yamashita; Ayes with reservations: none; 1 Noes: Representative(s) Rhoads; and 2 Excused: Representative(s) Saiki, Pine.",
