      "description": "Sets, for fiscal year 2010-2011 only, the employers' contribution at (1) 10.7% for police officers, firefighters, and corrections officers plus regular interest on the unfunded accrued liability for this group and (2) 6% for other employees plus regular interest on the unfunded accrued liability for this group."
