      "description": "Repeals the 07\/01\/09 \"sunset\" date in Act 53, SLH 2008, that established the misdemeanor offense of theft of beer keg and imposed recordkeeping requirements on scrap metal dealers that purchase beer kegs. Effective 06\/30\/09."
